close_reason: "Shipped runRegisteredCommandForTest SDK testing helper (src/sdk/testing.ts), exported from the sdk + sdk/testing barrels with CommandHandlerResult, wired an invoke step into the package scaffold sample test, and documented in SDK.md + EXTENSIONS.md. Completes the package-author testing loop: activate -> assertRegisteredCommandContract -> RUN -> deactivate. 100% coverage (4809 tests), verified end-to-end by scaffolding a package and running its generated node --test against the built SDK."
